      <span class="tip-box-ico">&#128161;</span>
      <p><strong>Timing tip:</strong> Take calm gummies 30-60 minutes before stressful situations — a work presentation, a difficult conversation, or a flight. For daily maintenance, morning or early afternoon dosing works best. None of the eight products below contain melatonin.</p>
    </div>

