    <p>Natural Vitality has been the dominant brand in the calm supplement space for over a decade, and their gummy format maintains the same core proposition that made the original CALM powder a household name: magnesium citrate at a meaningful dose. The 250mg per serving provides 60% of the recommended daily value — sufficient to address the subclinical deficiency that affects roughly half of all American adults.</p>

