    <p>Olly Goodbye Stress is the best-selling stress gummy in America for a reason: it attacks anxiety from three different angles. Ashwagandha modulates the HPA axis to lower cortisol. L-Theanine promotes alpha brain wave activity for calm alertness. GABA acts as an inhibitory neurotransmitter to quiet overactive neural signaling. The combination addresses both the hormonal and neurological dimensions of stress simultaneously.</p>

