    <p>If ashwagandha is your primary interest, Goli delivers the most potent dose on this list. At 600mg of KSM-66 per serving, this product matches or exceeds the dosing used in the majority of clinical trials demonstrating cortisol reduction. The addition of vitamin D is a thoughtful pairing — a 2020 meta-analysis in <em>Journal of Affective Disorders</em> found that vitamin D supplementation produced a significant reduction in depressive symptoms, and roughly 42% of American adults are deficient.</p>

    <div class="callout">
