    <p>Nature Made earns our Best Value designation not just because of the $0.20 per serving price point, but because that price comes with USP Verification — an independent certification that confirms the product contains what the label claims, is free from harmful contaminants, and was manufactured under GMP conditions. Fewer than 1% of supplements on the market carry the USP seal, making this a rare combination of affordability and verified quality.</p>

